<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.6">
<l>kūṉu lāviya maṭantaitaṉ koṭuñcoliṉ tiṟattiḷaṅ koṭiyōṭum</l>
<l>kāṉu lāviya karumukil tiruniṟat tavaṉiṭaṅ kaviṉārum</l>
<l>vāṉu lāviya matitavaḻ mālvarai māmatiḷ puṭaicūḻa</l>
<l>tēṉu lāviya ceḻumpoḻil taḻuviya tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the one with the divine hue of a dark cloud</l>
<l rend="indent">who walked in the forest along with the young creeper[-like lady],</l>
<l>Because of the harsh words of the woman who walked with a hump,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram which verdant groves, where nectar flows, embrace,</l>
<l>Its sides encircled by a great wall, [like a] dark mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the lovely full moon wanders the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
